<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Certificat – {{ formationTitre }}</title>
    <style>
        @page { margin: 0; size: A4 landscape; }

        @font-face {
            font-family: 'Radley';
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: normal;
            src: url('{{ fontRegular }}') format('truetype');
        }

        @font-face {
            font-family: 'Radley';
            font-style: italic;
            font-weight: normal;
            src: url('{{ fontItalic }}') format('truetype');
        }

        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

        html, body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: radley, serif;
            color: #3d3d56;
            background: #faf7f0;
        }

        .cert-sheet {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 842pt;
            height: 595pt;
            padding: 16pt;
            background: #faf7f0;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .cert-outer {
            position: relative;
            width: 810pt;
            height: 563pt;
            border: 1.5pt solid #667eea;
            background: #faf7f0;
        }

        /* Inset égal sur 4 côtés — évite le bug Dompdf du padding vertical sur table */
        .cert-inner {
            position: absolute;
            top: 12pt;
            left: 12pt;
            right: 12pt;
            bottom: 12pt;
            border: 2.5pt solid #764ba2;
            background: #faf7f0;
        }

        .cert-frame {
            position: relative;
            height: 100%;
            padding: 18pt 28pt 12pt;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .corner {
            position: absolute;
            width: 52pt;
            height: 52pt;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .corner-tl { top: 0; left: 0; }
        .corner-tr { top: 0; right: 0; }
        .corner-bl { bottom: 0; left: 0; }
        .corner-br { bottom: 0; right: 0; }

        .cert-header {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            margin-bottom: 6pt;
        }

        table.cert-header-row {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        table.cert-header-row td {
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        td.header-left { text-align: left; width: 55%; }
        td.header-right { text-align: right; width: 45%; }

        .header-brand-logo {
            width: 132pt;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
            margin-left: auto;
            background: transparent;
        }

        .header-platform {
            font-size: 7.5pt;
            color: #8888a0;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .header-brand {
            font-size: 11pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #5568d3;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .header-tagline {
            font-size: 7.5pt;
            color: #8888a0;
            font-style: italic;
        }

        table.layout {
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        table.layout td {
            vertical-align: top;
            text-align: center;
        }

        td.footer-cell {
            vertical-align: bottom;
            height: 1px;
            padding-top: 8pt;
        }

        .title-block { margin-top: 2pt; }

        .title-main {
            font-size: 30pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 4px;
            color: #3d3d56;
            line-height: 1;
        }

        .title-sub {
            font-size: 16pt;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #5568d3;
            margin-top: 4pt;
        }

        .title-deco {
            display: block;
            margin: 6pt auto 10pt;
        }

        .intro-line {
            font-size: 9pt;
            color: #4a4a68;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 8pt;
        }

        .recipient {
            font-size: 23pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #5568d3;
            line-height: 1.15;
            padding: 4pt 0 6pt;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .name-divider {
            width: 55%;
            margin: 0 auto 10pt;
            border-top: 1pt dotted #b8c0f0;
        }

        .body-text {
            font-size: 13pt;
            line-height: 1.5;
            color: #444460;
            padding: 0 20pt;
            margin: 0 auto;
            max-width: 520pt;
        }

        .body-text strong { color: #5568d3; }

        .fine-print {
            font-size: 11.5pt;
            line-height: 1.4;
            color: #8888a0;
            padding: 10pt 24pt 0;
            max-width: 520pt;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        table.footer-row {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        table.footer-row td {
            width: 33%;
            vertical-align: bottom;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0 8pt;
        }

        td.footer-left { text-align: left; }
        td.footer-right { text-align: right; }

        td.footer-center {
            vertical-align: top;
            text-align: center;
        }

        td.footer-labels-line {
            vertical-align: bottom;
            padding-top: 36pt;
        }

        .footer-date-label,
        .footer-delivered {
            font-size: 11pt;
            color: #666680;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }

        .footer-date-label {
            display: inline;
        }

        .footer-date-value {
            display: inline;
            font-size: 14pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1b294b;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-left: 5pt;
        }

        .footer-seal-block {
            text-align: center;
        }

        .validated-badge-img {
            width: 100pt;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
            margin: 2pt auto 0;
            background: transparent;
        }

        .seal-svg {
            width: 66pt;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .brand-logo-img {
            width: 175pt;
            height: auto;
            display: block;
            margin-left: auto;
            background: transparent;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="cert-sheet">
    <div class="cert-outer">
        <div class="cert-inner">
            <div class="cert-frame">
                {% include 'attestation/_corner_accents.html.twig' %}

                <div class="cert-header">
                    <table class="cert-header-row">
                        <tr>
                            <td class="header-left">
                                <div class="header-platform">{{ platformName }}</div>
                                <div class="header-brand">Lyceo Campus Numérique</div>
                                <div class="header-tagline">Modules professionnels en ligne</div>
                            </td>
                            <td class="header-right">
                                {% if lyceoBrandLogoPath %}
                                    <img src="{{ lyceoBrandLogoPath }}" class="header-brand-logo" alt="Lyceo Campus Numérique">
                                {% endif %}
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </div>

                <table class="layout">
                    <tr>
                        <td>
                            <div class="title-block">
                                <div class="title-main">CERTIFICAT</div>
                                <div class="title-sub">de Réussite</div>
                            </div>

                            {% include 'attestation/_title_decoration.html.twig' %}

                            <div class="intro-line">Nous certifions que</div>

                            <div class="recipient">{{ nomComplet }}</div>
                            <div class="name-divider"></div>

                            <p class="body-text">
                                a validé avec succès son parcours d'apprentissage, dispensé sur la plateforme
                                <strong>Lyceo Campus Numérique</strong>, conformément au programme établi dans la catégorie
                                <strong>{{ filiere }}</strong>.
                                Ce parcours comprend {{ nbChapitres }} chapitre{{ nbChapitres > 1 ? 's' : '' }}
                                et a été complété par la réussite du quiz final d'évaluation.
                            </p>

                            <p class="fine-print">
                                Ce certificat est délivré en reconnaissance de la réussite au quiz final
                                d'évaluation.
                                Félicitation pour votre réussite, nous vous attendons sur d'autres modules.
                            </p>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td class="footer-cell">
                            <table class="footer-row">
                                <tr>
                                    <td class="footer-left footer-labels-line">
                                        <span class="footer-date-label">Délivré le</span>
                                        <span class="footer-date-value">{{ dateCertificatFr }}</span>
                                    </td>
                                    <td rowspan="2" class="footer-center">
                                        <div class="footer-seal-block">
                                            {% include 'attestation/_seal_badge.html.twig' with { certYear: certYear, badgeAnneePath: badgeAnneePath } %}
                                            {% include 'attestation/_formation_validated_badge.html.twig' %}
                                        </div>
                                    </td>
                                    <td class="footer-right footer-labels-line">
                                        <span class="footer-delivered">Module validé</span>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td class="footer-left"></td>
                                    <td class="footer-right">
                                        {% include 'attestation/_lyceo_brand_pdf.html.twig' %}
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
